Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.75,0:00:04.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在『行动』的尽头
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.59,0:00:06.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有『结果』这个答案在等待
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.39,0:00:08.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,从未有过例外
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.94,0:00:11.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在那里 鲁路修的力量起不了作用
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.65,0:00:17.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,即使拥有着对任何对手都能下达绝对服从命令的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.19,0:00:20.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也无法从那个必然下逃脱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.64,0:00:23.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为了替母亲报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.35,0:00:29.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路修为了创造妹妹娜娜莉能幸福生活的世界而行动起来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.83,0:00:36.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是世界 人们却总是把和他的预想不同的结果摆在他眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.98,0:00:39.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,并追求结果的『继续』
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.05,0:00:43.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果这个『继续』与世界结合起来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.26,0:00:46.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,某些人必须背负的罪孽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.38,0:00:47.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所应得到的惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.00,0:00:50.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到底在何处呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.73,0:02:26.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fad(600,0)\pos(424,395)}STAGE 14
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.33,0:02:26.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fad(600,0)\pos(424,430)}GEASS 对 GEASS
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.14,0:02:27.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,指挥呼叫401
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.34,0:02:29.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,继续反击敌人并向9点方向移动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.01,0:02:31.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以后将归入西宁格卿的指挥下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.13,0:02:42.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.94,0:02:43.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别深追了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.10,0:02:46.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在保护总督是最优先的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.37,0:02:47.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.11,0:02:49.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,回话啊 ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.59,0:02:51.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,扇吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.72,0:02:53.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是我 C.C.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.41,0:02:54.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.63,0:02:56.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然没事但现在无法行动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.37,0:02:58.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你来发布撤退命令
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.37,0:02:59.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,迟疑的话会被全灭的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.14,0:03:01.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.69,0:03:02.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.17,0:03:05.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.84,0:03:07.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.56,0:03:10.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真少见啊 竟然动摇到无法发布指令
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.17,0:03:12.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是科奈莉娅的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.32,0:03:14.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的 枪不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.70,0:03:16.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在我晕过去的那段时间里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.55,0:03:17.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被什么人拿走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.08,0:03:19.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.48,0:03:21.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你的样子被人看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.67,0:03:23.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,至少被两个人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.05,0:03:25.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,开枪的和被射击的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.00,0:03:27.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有两个人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.40,0:03:35.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,莎莉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.48,0:03:39.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这么早你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.17,0:03:41.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,写信吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.00,0:03:43.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.25,0:03:46.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是情书之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.65,0:03:48.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对方是鲁路修吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.41,0:03:52.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.06,0:03:56.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想见由菲米娅殿下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.94,0:03:59.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢…想说一下感谢的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.05,0:04:04.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,饭店劫持事件时她挺身保护了妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.55,0:04:07.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说出自己是由菲米娅 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.41,0:04:08.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.42,0:04:09.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.55,0:04:10.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.45,0:04:11.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为是公主啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.05,0:04:13.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能入赘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.43,0:04:16.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为有这种不单纯的思想的话是见不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.50,0:04:17.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不单纯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.37,0:04:20.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜莉还真是严格啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.98,0:04:22.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧 会长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.90,0:04:24.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算鲁路修不介意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.91,0:04:27.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但你也别把这种越线的行为冲着我来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.50,0:04:30.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我也想见一见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.85,0:04:32.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想见由菲米娅殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.65,0:04:35.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.79,0:04:39.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 对方是高不可攀的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.73,0:04:44.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是阿修佛德学园学生会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.45,0:04:48.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.90,0:04:49.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.03,0:04:52.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你那儿有什么不平常的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.14,0:04:53.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.19,0:04:55.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你不在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.77,0:04:56.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.97,0:04:59.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,莎莉好像也没有出现
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.89,0:05:02.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最近上课也请假
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.28,0:05:04.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你还是要做的更像学生一点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.16,0:05:07.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 你这个优等生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.62,0:05:09.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能转告一下娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.52,0:05:11.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天会晚回来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.51,0:05:13.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是“今天会”而是“今天也”吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.90,0:05:15.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老是见不到面的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.47,0:05:17.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要在同一所学校啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.40,0:05:17.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.14,0:05:19.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.74,0:05:20.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.83,0:05:21.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 阿瑟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.23,0:05:25.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在玩什么啊 那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.94,0:05:27.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看这个情况
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.36,0:05:29.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 朱雀好像不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.68,0:05:32.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这么一来被军队看到的可能消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.79,0:05:37.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不认为军队和黑色骑士团以外还有人会去那个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.02,0:05:41.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也有日本解放战线的幸存者这一可能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.68,0:05:43.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只偷了枪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.33,0:05:46.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我让扇注意黑市的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.31,0:05:47.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,血样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.44,0:05:49.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然采取了但太花时间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.44,0:05:54.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还有就是好像在战场上看到了莎莉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.33,0:05:56.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 和你接吻的那个女人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.90,0:05:58.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你真烦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.61,0:06:00.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只是想确认一下 你这个好色的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.91,0:06:01.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.81,0:06:05.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是这样的话她就是我们现在的主要目标
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.10,0:06:09.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不论是这次的作战还是成田连山
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.01,0:06:12.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明显是针对公主的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.03,0:06:15.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,瞄准首领是战争的正统方案
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.47,0:06:17.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,克洛维斯殿下的事也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.97,0:06:21.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,与其说ZERO对于布里塔尼亚的体制
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.29,0:06:25.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还不如说他可能是以对布里塔尼亚皇族的仇恨来行动的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.25,0:06:26.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,仇恨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.40,0:06:27.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由菲米娅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.74,0:06:30.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为了保护人质而挺身而出吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.21,0:06:31.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还是老样子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.54,0:06:34.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小心啊 由菲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.92,0:06:37.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不想再见到饭店劫持那样的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.93,0:06:39.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要招入骑士呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.85,0:06:40.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.15,0:06:43.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,作为警卫的由菲米娅大人的专任骑士的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.23,0:06:47.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就能以那人为中心构筑亲卫队
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.71,0:06:49.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由菲米娅大人是副总督
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.07,0:06:51.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,应该已经有那样的权利了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.71,0:06:57.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最初认为他只是比较温柔的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.53,0:07:02.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你不认为他对人命的态度太过激了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.84,0:07:03.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.85,0:07:05.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,启动数据并没有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.03,0:07:08.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我还想顺便试一下那个东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.22,0:07:10.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但那还在调整中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.90,0:07:14.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还有你完全不顾我说的不要把朱雀当成零件
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.83,0:07:18.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不好好面对他的话会无法看清一切 无法好好传达的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.46,0:07:22.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 你才是没有把他和某人重叠起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.23,0:07:24.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.72,0:07:25.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.24,0:07:28.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你还真是能注意到奇怪的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.54,0:07:31.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么说我也是你的上司啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.95,0:07:35.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在这种地方干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.04,0:07:39.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在等房间的杀菌消毒结束
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.93,0:07:43.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我非得检查别人的内衣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.16,0:07:45.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个人情可是很贵的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.99,0:07:47.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.29,0:07:49.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 你干的还真快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.81,0:07:52.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个女人应该不会介意让喜欢的男人来…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.40,0:07:53.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.52,0:07:55.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你又对奇怪的地方过于执着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.72,0:07:58.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 没找到枪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.84,0:08:01.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,日记也只写到14天以前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.46,0:08:02.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,14天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.37,0:08:03.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.30,0:08:05.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她父亲死去的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.04,0:08:09.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.40,0:08:11.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是你的照片啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.62,0:08:12.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.47,0:08:13.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是很可爱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.11,0:08:15.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,作为嫌疑犯来说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.59,0:08:17.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别用这种说法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.86,0:08:23.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,成田
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.39,0:08:38.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.52,0:08:39.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.13,0:08:42.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.17,0:08:47.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不错的慰灵碑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.94,0:08:50.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,莎莉·菲耐特小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.00,0:08:51.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.72,0:08:55.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是可惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.44,0:08:56.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只差一点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.50,0:08:58.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下次连那白壳的家伙也一起打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.74,0:08:59.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别介意了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.78,0:09:00.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.71,0:09:02.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,玉成一下子就被干掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.67,0:09:06.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,解放战线的船
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.57,0:09:09.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么爆炸了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.35,0:09:10.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,自爆了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.99,0:09:12.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有过联络吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.34,0:09:13.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快来救援
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.39,0:09:15.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为了那个ZERO才行动的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.63,0:09:16.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 对了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.61,0:09:18.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是见到脸的机会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.40,0:09:21.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你在怀疑ZERO吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.44,0:09:22.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.93,0:09:25.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还是说时机太巧了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.37,0:09:29.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果那是ZERO所做的话你想怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.22,0:09:30.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊 那种口气
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.86,0:09:31.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 迪哈鲁特
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.12,0:09:34.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,之前你好像害怕的逃跑了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.66,0:09:36.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还真是胆小的布里塔尼亚人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.78,0:09:39.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别用这种口气对我们干部说话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.43,0:09:41.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想要掌握战场的情况而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.13,0:09:44.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,扇也承认了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.10,0:09:46.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.98,0:09:48.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO也说没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.12,0:09:51.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜欢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.23,0:09:54.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,叫莎莉的那个女人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.93,0:09:55.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.02,0:09:57.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.95,0:09:59.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.32,0:10:01.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么为什么要去成田
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.28,0:10:04.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,当然是因为有可能被知道了身份
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.77,0:10:06.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.78,0:10:07.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,解决掉她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.14,0:10:11.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真正不想失去的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.40,0:10:12.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就应该远离她
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.74,0:10:16.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是经验吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.04,0:10:18.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.36,0:10:19.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是生存的方式
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.62,0:10:23.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路修真是过分的男人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.49,0:10:25.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你对鲁路的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.32,0:10:26.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你被骗了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.14,0:10:28.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他其实是ZERO的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.55,0:10:31.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.39,0:10:35.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他用下令造成你父亲死去的那张嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.26,0:10:37.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夺去了你的吻哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.41,0:10:39.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,无法原谅呢 这样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.56,0:10:42.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要受到惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.14,0:10:44.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他和你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.26,0:10:46.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.54,0:10:47.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我全部都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.25,0:10:50.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那天晚上的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.28,0:10:56.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙是ZERO吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.33,0:11:04.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这真是让人吃惊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.23,0:11:06.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,学生自己是ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.53,0:11:08.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还是布里塔尼亚人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.89,0:11:14.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要把这家伙交给科奈莉娅总督
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.45,0:11:16.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我就能成为贵族了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.25,0:11:19.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不只是骑士侯而是真正的贵族
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.01,0:11:21.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且他还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.12,0:11:23.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.57,0:11:25.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么样的处刑会比较适合呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.74,0:11:28.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总督也会对你…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.35,0:11:31.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.94,0:11:33.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为他是你的男人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.92,0:11:38.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是杀人犯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.49,0:11:39.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和ZERO同罪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.21,0:11:42.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 我是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.87,0:11:46.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且以父亲的死作为交换代价
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.28,0:11:50.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 我是 我是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.13,0:11:52.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,狡猾的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.89,0:11:57.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为了期待从他那里得到温柔故意表现得很可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.25,0:11:58.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不对…不对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.48,0:12:00.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,同情的视线很舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.02,0:12:01.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.22,0:12:04.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想要装成悲剧的女主角到什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.63,0:12:06.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我没想过那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.42,0:12:09.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为了救男人而杀人的你不是什么女主角
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.05,0:12:11.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而是丑恶的魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.95,0:12:14.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 我是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.34,0:12:17.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,即使知道鲁路修喜欢别的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.73,0:12:19.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也想呆在他的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.49,0:12:23.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该受到报应
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.98,0:12:30.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想要一生背负这种心情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.78,0:12:32.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只有一个人来背负
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.15,0:12:36.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,无法弥补罪孽就无法解脱内心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.73,0:12:39.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你和鲁路修真是太可怜了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.67,0:12:51.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,本来认为会是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.16,0:12:52.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只有分头去找了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.08,0:12:55.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道吧 莎莉的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.14,0:12:56.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你到现在还说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.98,0:13:01.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可能性很低
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.63,0:13:02.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,应该不会在的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.20,0:13:05.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被知道了的话怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.34,0:13:06.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,解决掉她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.65,0:13:07.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.87,0:13:09.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,应该还有一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.75,0:13:10.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.14,0:13:12.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙和莎莉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.42,0:13:14.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静下来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.41,0:13:15.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,重新再从头
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.96,0:13:19.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,莎莉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.10,0:13:21.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.26,0:13:22.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在你在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.36,0:13:24.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你说在哪儿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.95,0:13:26.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.91,0:13:31.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.93,0:13:33.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对莎莉做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.67,0:13:35.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.28,0:13:36.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可怕的表情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.72,0:13:39.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,无法原谅自己的女人被夺走的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.04,0:13:41.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,莎莉在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.35,0:13:42.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你想知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.63,0:13:44.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么来决胜负吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.08,0:13:47.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你对这个比较在行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.91,0:13:54.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没有照片
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.12,0:13:55.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要我画的话能用巴土安画风
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.12,0:13:55.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[巴土安画风(Batuan style):巴厘岛的一种绘画流派风格]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.05,0:13:57.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,让我等到你画完吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.13,0:13:59.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还是算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.21,0:14:01.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托军队或警察的话会比较快
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.82,0:14:04.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不想招惹没有必要的危险
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.41,0:14:06.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么到高处去找怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.03,0:14:08.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了 算了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.52,0:14:12.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路修这家伙在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.63,0:14:18.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.57,0:14:19.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,毛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.98,0:14:25.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是这家伙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.06,0:14:27.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,另一个目击者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.11,0:14:31.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下棋估计只是一个幌子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.11,0:14:36.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的目的是把我带到无人的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.41,0:14:39.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是第一次玩这个游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.55,0:14:41.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,使用手机只是演戏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.67,0:14:44.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 是因为不知道我的长相
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.55,0:14:48.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说没有时间得到我的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.84,0:14:50.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是周详准备过的作战
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.29,0:14:52.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.63,0:14:54.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会有破绽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.75,0:14:57.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还是把注意力集中在胜负上比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.04,0:14:59.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,会输的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.40,0:15:02.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么第一次玩 你这个骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.38,0:15:07.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.74,0:15:08.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.57,0:15:11.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不 正是因为是你所以才胜不了毛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.03,0:15:17.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.29,0:15:18.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我会
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.91,0:15:24.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 这样可以算是我的胜利吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.28,0:15:28.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我竟然会被完全看穿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.92,0:15:30.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.60,0:15:32.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你没听C.C.说过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.97,0:15:35.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.56,0:15:36.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对于我的真实身份
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.47,0:15:39.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然在一瞬间想到了14种答案
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.91,0:15:43.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且其中之一是完全正确
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.04,0:15:45.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Geass能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.93,0:15:50.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你的Geass如果没有直接看到对方的眼睛就没法使用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.63,0:15:53.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这些规则我也全都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.70,0:15:54.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能读出我的思想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.90,0:15:57.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的就是这样的Geass
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.50,0:15:58.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你对莎莉开枪了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.05,0:16:01.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你对莎莉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.33,0:16:02.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.72,0:16:05.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,莎莉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.03,0:16:06.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.16,0:16:09.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,开始惩罚游戏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.26,0:16:12.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.42,0:16:14.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天的你不像平常的你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.15,0:16:17.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会有这种感觉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.85,0:16:22.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.24,0:16:25.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,坚持住
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.17,0:16:27.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.98,0:16:30.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.30,0:16:31.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.34,0:16:34.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.25,0:16:38.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,莎莉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.59,0:16:39.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这把枪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.63,0:16:43.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO的…鲁路的枪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.50,0:16:46.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,用Geass吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.69,0:16:49.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该还没对她用过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.33,0:16:54.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过如果你这么做的话就会马上开枪的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.80,0:16:56.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能看透的只是表象吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.18,0:16:59.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有和我一样使用Geass的条件吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.89,0:17:00.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,发动时机
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.89,0:17:01.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,持续时间呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.00,0:17:03.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他有什么目的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.04,0:17:05.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果想要杀掉我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.99,0:17:07.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,多想想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.73,0:17:09.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,用你得意的策略
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.43,0:17:10.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咕噜咕噜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.09,0:17:11.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.02,0:17:15.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对于当小偷的猫来说这种死法才适合
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.56,0:17:17.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.15,0:17:19.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.46,0:17:21.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,补偿自己的罪孽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.53,0:17:23.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也会陪你一起死的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.98,0:17:24.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.64,0:17:26.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她也开枪了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.71,0:17:28.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对另一个目击者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.65,0:17:30.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为了保护你的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.82,0:17:32.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说来 那个血迹是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.81,0:17:35.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,结束吧 鲁路
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.61,0:17:36.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.62,0:17:38.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对于罪孽就是要用惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.35,0:17:39.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙对莎莉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.45,0:17:41.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能够读懂思考的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.93,0:17:44.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,操纵人 对其进行诱导就很简单
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.79,0:17:45.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 正是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.14,0:17:47.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别被骗了 莎莉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.95,0:17:48.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.84,0:17:50.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 那是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.81,0:17:52.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,骗了她的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.88,0:17:53.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.88,0:17:55.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了人是罪的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.49,0:17:56.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就不要再让罪孽增加了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.90,0:17:58.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不错 真会说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.75,0:18:01.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的杀了人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.51,0:18:03.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你不会是被那家伙诱导了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.25,0:18:06.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她是自己发觉的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.65,0:18:09.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一直隐瞒下去是没有意义的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.54,0:18:10.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没有那样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.65,0:18:11.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,莎莉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.41,0:18:12.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.32,0:18:36.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在犹豫什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.97,0:18:39.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙可是杀了你的父亲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.62,0:18:40.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.56,0:18:42.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙只是杀人凶手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.47,0:18:43.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.56,0:18:46.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,莎莉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.34,0:18:46.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.21,0:18:48.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.58,0:18:50.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊 这女人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.50,0:18:52.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,思考真是乱的一塌糊涂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.26,0:18:53.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,算了 我来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.40,0:18:56.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.05,0:18:59.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.29,0:19:01.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下就随你们两个人的便吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.68,0:19:06.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,莎莉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.10,0:19:09.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.24,0:19:10.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,本来还想弄得戏剧性一点的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.11,0:19:12.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然很无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.89,0:19:13.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就把两个人一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.78,0:19:16.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.80,0:19:18.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我竟然没有发觉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.05,0:19:21.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.07,0:19:25.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,C.C.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.96,0:19:27.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.13,0:19:29.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,终于见到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.40,0:19:31.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你 真正的你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.78,0:19:33.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,起来了吗 毛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.80,0:19:35.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 毛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.10,0:19:39.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 毛 你不是能行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.29,0:19:41.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 毛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.70,0:19:45.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这种打扮也很美啊 C.C.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.07,0:19:47.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,C.C. 我会来见你的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.90,0:19:49.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就会来见你的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.50,0:19:51.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一定 一定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.00,0:19:52.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,毛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.64,0:19:57.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你竟然会出现在人群之中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.48,0:19:58.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,莎莉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.76,0:19:59.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已经够了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.90,0:20:00.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.78,0:20:01.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.53,0:20:03.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我开枪射了人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.63,0:20:04.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.64,0:20:05.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.92,0:20:07.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,莎莉没有错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.88,0:20:10.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我还开枪射了鲁路
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.30,0:20:11.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.94,0:20:14.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我射了鲁路
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.73,0:20:15.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我原谅你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.76,0:20:18.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你的罪全部由我来承担
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.44,0:20:20.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想要你对我温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.65,0:20:22.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这有什么不对的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.40,0:20:24.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸明明死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.38,0:20:25.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,忘了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.69,0:20:28.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌的事全部忘记就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.27,0:20:29.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.24,0:20:30.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.72,0:20:33.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我来让你全部忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.46,0:20:34.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.02,0:20:36.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,莎莉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.36,0:20:38.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你父亲的事很对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.25,0:20:40.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能够重生一次的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.23,0:20:42.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.13,0:20:42.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.96,0:20:44.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.27,0:20:55.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.49,0:20:57.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你也失去了家人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.19,0:21:00.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不是家人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.01,0:21:03.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.56,0:21:07.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 大概是很重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.01,0:21:09.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.68,0:21:14.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有些事是失去之后才第一次明白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.19,0:21:19.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,自己曾那么的被她的笑容所拯救
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.12,0:21:25.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,像那样的拌嘴也能笑着去回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.36,0:21:27.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜欢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.42,0:21:28.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.35,0:21:31.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.77,0:21:34.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已经不知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.98,0:21:37.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,黎明一定会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.02,0:21:44.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我虽然已经忘了到刚才为止自己为什么要到这儿来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.27,0:21:49.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定这也是什么契机
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.33,0:21:52.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,当然不可能忘掉想忘掉的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.58,0:21:54.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也有很多悲伤的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.20,0:21:57.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是黎明总是会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.00,0:22:00.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以别再一直消沉下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.68,0:22:01.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.00,0:22:04.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是这么认为的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.99,0:22:05.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一直以来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.99,0:22:07.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.86,0:23:52.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也许我是比较天真
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.49,0:23:55.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也许除掉莎莉更好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.82,0:23:56.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.45,0:24:01.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Geass 如果说这个力量会使人孤独的话
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.59,0:24:04.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我必须要有更能忍受的精神才行
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.56,0:24:07.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然后对毛 把这个仇…
